    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Cerealian Clan, Level 8+<br />You live for the perfect shot, not letting anything get in your way. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Intelligence score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>When you make a ranged ninjutsu attack using your Cerealian hijutsu, they cannot suffer disadvantage from being within 5 feet of your target.</li><li>Cerealian hijutsu has a max critical threat range bonus of +5.</li><li>When you cast a Cerealian hijutsu and land critical hit, you can also double any flat damage bonus given in the jutsu.</li></ul>",
